THIRD-PARTY DATA AND LICENSING NOTICE

This repository is engineered to be "real" while respecting licensing
boundaries. In particular:

  - ICD-10-CM and HCPCS content are public-domain subsets (CMS / NCHS).
  - CPT codes are shown as a clearly-labeled DEMO placeholder: real numbers
    with our own descriptors, NOT the copyrighted AMA CPT text. A licensed
    AMA CPT distribution must be supplied for any production use.
  - NCCI / MUE edits are modeled on public CMS edit logic (a subset).
  - The clinical ontology is a small demo set; production deployments are
    expected to license SNOMED CT and/or UMLS.
  - All patient charts in this build are synthetic and contain no PHI.

